# Code Review Gate

Before approving any PR:

- [ ] Matches acceptance criteria and glossary terms
- [ ] Tests added/updated; CI green
- [ ] No secrets, no debug flags enabled in prod config
- [ ] Tenant isolation considered
- [ ] ADR/docs updated if architecture changed
- [ ] Diff is focused — no unrelated changes

Feedback format:
- **Blocker:** must fix
- **Should:** strongly recommend
- **Nit:** optional

